201
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:25,550
Pei Shen

202
00:11:28,720 --> 00:11:29,510
passed away.

203
00:11:31,270 --> 00:11:32,240
He committed suicide.

204
00:11:32,790 --> 00:11:33,960
We couldn't figure out

205
00:11:34,571 --> 00:11:35,840
why a man who was bold enough

206
00:11:35,910 --> 00:11:37,510
to kidnap someone in the previous second

207
00:11:37,720 --> 00:11:39,910
