213
00:11:52,870 --> 00:11:54,960
Xi Lin, have you ever thought

214
00:11:55,750 --> 00:11:57,630
that Pei Shen actually liked you?

215
00:12:00,200 --> 00:12:01,550
How is that possible?

216
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:03,320
I haven't even seen him.

217
00:12:03,550 --> 00:12:06,240
Besides, I didn't even know the presence

218
00:12:06,240 --> 00:12:07,720
of my father's subordinate before that.

219
00:12:11,510 --> 00:12:12,150
Well,

220
00:12:12,910 --> 00:12:14,200
could he be

221
00:12:14,720 --> 00:12:16,750
stalking me in hiding all this while?

222
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:24,000
I understand.

223
00:12:25,150 --> 00:12:26,550
Because of my father,

224
00:12:27,910 --> 00:12:29,480
