get suspicious of me.

225
00:12:31,550 --> 00:12:32,510
However, Ziqi,

226
00:12:33,440 --> 00:12:34,910
you should know me well.

227
00:12:35,320 --> 00:12:36,630
No matter when,

228
00:12:37,960 --> 00:12:40,240
I won't let anyone hurt you.

229
00:12:45,960 --> 00:12:46,840
You talk first.

230
00:12:47,150 --> 00:12:48,270
I need to take a call.

231
00:12:48,960 --> 00:12:49,750
Go ahead.

232
00:13:01,150 --> 00:13:01,870
Hello?

233
00:13:02,480 --> 00:13:03,200
Hello.

234
00:13:04,670 --> 00:13:06,120
