235
00:13:08,080 --> 00:13:09,150
Who did it?

236
00:13:09,750 --> 00:13:10,550
It was Xi Lin.

237
00:13:11,670 --> 00:13:12,670
Of course.

238
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:16,630
Actually, in the beginning,
I could clearly feel

239
00:13:17,150 --> 00:13:19,320
that Pei Shen wanted to
drag me down with him

240
00:13:19,790 --> 00:13:21,390
but you mentioned Xi Lin

241
00:13:21,720 --> 00:13:22,750
and that triggered him,

242
00:13:23,670 --> 00:13:25,030
hence he pushed me away

243
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:26,270
