245
00:13:29,440 --> 00:13:30,150
He seemed so polite

246
00:13:30,150 --> 00:13:31,630
at the company before.

247
00:13:31,790 --> 00:13:32,670
After all, he is someone

248
00:13:32,670 --> 00:13:33,870
