253
00:13:44,390 --> 00:13:46,150
Could that person be Xi Lin?

254
00:13:47,080 --> 00:13:48,200
You can test it out.

255
00:13:50,030 --> 00:13:53,200
Alright, I know what to do now.

256
00:13:53,630 --> 00:13:54,390
Yuan Xia,

257
00:13:56,120 --> 00:13:57,240
