to drive like that.

261
00:14:17,480 --> 00:14:18,270
Ziqi,

262
00:14:21,240 --> 00:14:23,270
I dropped the phone
by accident and it broke.

263
00:14:24,840 --> 00:14:25,630
What should we do?

264
00:14:31,790 --> 00:14:32,550
It's fine.

265
00:14:32,960 --> 00:14:35,080
We're getting it destroyed soon anyway.

266
00:14:35,171 --> 00:14:37,142
I'll take care of it
at the company tomorrow.

267
00:14:37,320 --> 00:14:38,457
We won't need it anymore.

268
00:14:39,630 --> 00:14:40,390
It's fine.

269
00:14:42,840 --> 00:14:43,630
Xi Lin,

270
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:45,840
