00:15:29,960 --> 00:15:31,630
It happened at the fork of the road

285
00:15:31,630 --> 00:15:32,942
at the foot of Stargazing Station.

286
00:15:33,200 --> 00:15:35,080
I was turning
and she was going the opposite way.

287
00:15:35,550 --> 00:15:37,080
Both our cars would collide head-on.

288
00:15:37,480 --> 00:15:39,030
I died on the spot.

289
00:15:40,080 --> 00:15:42,030
You from a year later even asked me
to tell you

290
00:15:42,390 --> 00:15:43,840
that what he regretted most

291
00:15:44,320 --> 00:15:45,550
was letting me drive.

292
00:15:46,360 --> 00:15:47,960
He said he was not a good coach

293
00:15:48,028 --> 00:15:49,840
and shouldn't have taught me
to drive like that.

294
00:15:51,000 --> 00:15:53,114
However, what does that have
anything to do with you?

295
00:15:53,510 --> 00:15:56,240
It's foul luck at best,

296
00:15:56,790 --> 00:15:58,440
being targeted by a psychotic.

297
00:16:00,440 --> 00:16:01,480
Speaking of this,

298
00:16:01,480 --> 00:16:03,240
Xi Lin's really persistent with me.

299
00:16:03,771 --> 00:16:06,270
Those who didn't know would think
she was going to commit suicide.

300
00:16:11,750 --> 00:16:14,720
By the way, there's something else
I find strange.

301
00:16:15,320 --> 00:16:17,200
I noticed many gifts

302
00:16:17,200 --> 00:16:18,750
in the corridor of Xi Lin's house.

303
00:16:26,480 --> 00:16:27,840
These are the gifts Ms. Xi prepared

304
00:16:27,840 --> 00:16:29,550
for her friend's birthday.

305
00:16:29,550 --> 00:16:31,240
Why aren't they sent out?

306
00:16:31,790 --> 00:16:33,000
I'm not sure why either,

307
00:16:33,000 --> 00:16:34,910
but these are quite expensive gifts.

308
00:16:35,000 --> 00:16:36,910
She would come over from time to time
to take a look

309
00:16:37,200 --> 00:16:38,670
and we aren't allowed to touch them.

310
00:16:41,150 --> 00:16:42,200
Does she

311
00:16:42,390 --> 00:16:44,750
give you birthday presents every year?

312
00:16:46,360 --> 00:16:48,440
But I returned all of them.

313
00:16:48,510 --> 00:16:51,270
Are you sure
you return them every year?

314
00:16:56,960 --> 00:17:02,030
I'm not too sure
about the year my father died.

315
00:17:02,030 --> 00:17:04,160
I spent the year in misery

316
00:17:04,880 --> 00:17:06,160
so I didn't care about this.

317
00:17:10,400 --> 00:17:11,750
The gift I received that year

318
00:17:11,750 --> 00:17:13,590
is sealed together with
my father's belongings.

319
00:17:13,590 --> 00:17:15,057
Otherwise, I won't be able to find it.

320
00:17:23,160 --> 00:17:25,000
To Ziqi: Happy birthday.

321
00:17:25,000 --> 00:17:26,830
This is my favorite

322
00:17:26,830 --> 00:17:28,720
and most satisfying gift of the year.

323
00:17:28,720 --> 00:17:30,230
I'm giving it to you.
I hope you like it.

324
00:17:30,240 --> 00:17:31,030
From Xi Lin.

325
00:17:41,270 --> 00:17:42,070
Wait.

326
00:17:47,590 --> 00:17:49,030
This is a bracelet

327
00:17:49,350 --> 00:17:50,640
that I made with my own hands.

328
00:17:52,160 --> 00:17:54,030
I also personally gave it to Mr. Heng

329
00:17:54,070 --> 00:17:55,830
on the night of your birthday.

330
00:17:56,720 --> 00:17:58,440
I made this bracelet myself.

331
00:17:58,440 --> 00:17:59,480
You take it first.

332
00:17:59,480 --> 00:18:01,510
Please pass this to him
when you see him.

333
00:18:02,000 --> 00:18:04,200
I wish him to be happy
every day in the future.

334
00:18:06,400 --> 00:18:07,070
Sure.

335
00:18:15,310 --> 00:18:17,350
My father won't pass Xi Lin

336
00:18:17,350 --> 00:18:18,440
something you gifted.

337
00:18:19,070 --> 00:18:21,110
How did this thing
fall into her hands, then?

338
00:18:21,550 --> 00:18:22,750
It's impossible

339
00:18:22,750 --> 00:18:24,680
that she picked it up by chance, right?

340
00:18:26,590 --> 00:18:27,400
No way.

341
00:18:28,200 --> 00:18:29,440
Someone like Xi Lin

342
00:18:29,640 --> 00:18:31,510
wouldn't gift something
she picked up by chance

343
00:18:31,880 --> 00:18:34,110
to someone she likes.

344
00:18:35,510 --> 00:18:36,310
You have a point.

345
00:18:37,960 --> 00:18:39,440
This is peculiar.

346
00:18:39,500 --> 00:18:41,070
In fact, the psychological aspect
of this

347
00:18:41,070 --> 00:18:41,960
is easy to explain.

348
00:18:41,960 --> 00:18:43,960
When a murderer

349
00:18:44,000 --> 00:18:45,480
with sociopathic traits kills,

350
00:18:45,550 --> 00:18:47,550
he will remove objects from the victims

351
00:18:47,550 --> 00:18:48,880
to collect them as trophies.

352
00:18:49,110 --> 00:18:52,200
Are you saying that Mr. Heng...

353
00:18:54,550 --> 00:18:55,480
Impossible.

354
00:18:55,590 --> 00:18:56,920
They have no grudges.

355
00:18:56,920 --> 00:18:58,750
I have a guess.

356
00:18:58,750 --> 00:18:59,960
Just listen and judge.

357
00:19:00,030 --> 00:19:02,030
Mr. Wei from a year later
called and said

358
00:19:02,030 --> 00:19:05,270
that Xi Lin would murder
Yuan Xia in 2025,

359
00:19:05,270 --> 00:19:05,880
right?

360
00:19:05,880 --> 00:19:07,510
Her motive would be you.

361
00:19:07,920 --> 00:19:09,880
Similarly, the reason
she attacked your father

362
00:19:10,070 --> 00:19:11,310
could be because of you, too.

363
00:19:12,000 --> 00:19:13,640
I've seen a very typical case of

364
00:19:13,680 --> 00:19:15,240
antisocial personality disorder

365
00:19:15,240 --> 00:19:16,640
in my psychology class before.

366
00:19:16,960 --> 00:19:19,200
To get closer to the crush,

367
00:19:19,270 --> 00:19:21,270
the murderer killed her whole family.

368
00:19:21,590 --> 00:19:23,510
His purpose is to make himself

369
00:19:23,510 --> 00:19:26,440
the only person his crush
can rely on in this world.

370
00:19:26,720 --> 00:19:27,960
Isn't that sick?

371
00:19:28,114 --> 00:19:30,240
Yes, it is indeed a mental condition
in medical terms.

372
00:19:30,440 --> 00:19:32,200
Besides, when Xi Lin was hospitalized,

373
00:19:32,200 --> 00:19:33,920
we gave her a psychological evaluation.

374
00:19:34,240 --> 00:19:36,790
I remember my colleague
complained to me that Xi Lin

375
00:19:37,000 --> 00:19:38,960
was the most self-centered person
he had ever seen.

376
00:19:38,971 --> 00:19:40,885
There's no way
that she'd commit suicide.

377
00:19:42,350 --> 00:19:44,030
If it's really like you said

378
00:19:44,680 --> 00:19:46,350
that it was Xi Lin who killed my father,

379
00:19:47,880 --> 00:19:49,270
then she's pretty good.

380
00:19:50,480 --> 00:19:52,240
Xi Kun and Pei Shen

381
00:19:52,240 --> 00:19:53,750
were blamed for everything,

382
00:19:55,030 --> 00:19:56,350
and she was totally fine.

383
00:20:02,160 --> 00:20:03,310
She won't be fine.

384
00:20:05,310 --> 00:20:07,030
I will make her show her true colors.

385
00:20:09,030 --> 00:20:10,790
According to Dr. Xing's analysis,

386
00:20:10,790 --> 00:20:12,830
if Xi Lin has an antisocial personality,

387
00:20:13,680 --> 00:20:15,240
she will definitely not allow me

388
00:20:15,240 --> 00:20:17,200
to continue to stay by your side.

389
00:20:17,830 --> 00:20:19,240
Besides, I guess she was the one

390
00:20:19,480 --> 00:20:21,790
who picked up
when Pei Shen made the call

391
00:20:22,720 --> 00:20:24,160
before the accident in Lin County.

392
00:20:24,480 --> 00:20:26,270
When you first reached out to me

393
00:20:26,400 --> 00:20:28,790
and placed the bellflowers in my hand,

394
00:20:28,790 --> 00:20:31,240
I could do anything for you.

395
00:20:32,000 --> 00:20:33,310
So Xi Lin

396
00:20:33,310 --> 00:20:35,400
is the one who really wants to kill me.

397
00:20:36,400 --> 00:20:37,640
If I guessed correctly,

398
00:20:38,114 --> 00:20:40,914
she must already know the existence of
the dual space-time phone.

399
00:20:41,640 --> 00:20:42,960
So she will definitely find a way

400
00:20:43,550 --> 00:20:45,030
to cut us off from the future

401
00:20:45,200 --> 00:20:47,030
before she kills me.

402
00:20:48,310 --> 00:20:49,510
No wonder you let her find out

403
00:20:50,000 --> 00:20:52,310
that we planned to destroy the phone
at her house.

404
00:20:53,485 --> 00:20:54,742
To force her to take action.

405
00:20:55,510 --> 00:20:56,200
Yes.

406
00:20:56,510 --> 00:20:58,680
She won't watch the phone
getting destroyed

407
00:20:58,680 --> 00:21:00,110
without any action.

408
00:21:00,110 --> 00:21:00,920
Of course.

409
00:21:01,550 --> 00:21:02,920
The phone is just the first step.

410
00:21:03,440 --> 00:21:04,550
More importantly,

411
00:21:04,714 --> 00:21:07,028
we have to catch the evidence
of her committing murder.

412
00:21:08,880 --> 00:21:10,270
Yuan Xia, I know what you're thinking

413
00:21:10,270 --> 00:21:11,440
but I disagree.

414
00:21:11,720 --> 00:21:13,830
If she is really like what I said,

415
00:21:13,830 --> 00:21:15,200
then she is extremely dangerous.

416
00:21:15,240 --> 00:21:16,550
We can think about it first.

417
00:21:16,750 --> 00:21:17,830
There could be other ways.

418
00:21:17,830 --> 00:21:19,440
She will go abroad soon.

419
00:21:19,440 --> 00:21:20,790
Isn't she going to kill me?

420
00:21:20,960 --> 00:21:22,350
Just let her do it.

421
00:21:22,350 --> 00:21:23,257
But this time,

422
00:21:23,260 --> 00:21:25,240
we have to make her
follow our script to kill me.

423
00:21:25,240 --> 00:21:26,000
No.

424
00:21:26,640 --> 00:21:28,680
Ziqi, I know what you are worried about.

425
00:21:28,680 --> 00:21:30,000
You don't want me to take risks

426
00:21:30,000 --> 00:21:31,920
but I really can't sit still
and wait for death.

427
00:21:32,240 --> 00:21:33,440
From our first time

428
00:21:33,590 --> 00:21:35,550
trying to change my ending until now,

429
00:21:35,550 --> 00:21:36,790
all our efforts have been in vain.

430
00:21:36,790 --> 00:21:38,350
It's like the universe is telling us

431
00:21:38,350 --> 00:21:39,960
that everything is already fixed.

432
00:21:40,142 --> 00:21:41,310
So I'm willing to take the risk

433
00:21:41,880 --> 00:21:43,030
this time around.

434
00:21:44,000 --> 00:21:46,030
I don't want to be frightened anymore.

