00:22:21,310 --> 00:22:22,790
(that what you regretted most)

442
00:22:23,240 --> 00:22:24,510
(was letting me drive.)

443
00:22:25,350 --> 00:22:26,960
(He said he was not a good coach)

444
00:22:27,070 --> 00:22:29,114
(and shouldn't have taught me
to drive like that.)

445
00:22:31,510 --> 00:22:32,440
(Drive?)

446
00:22:33,830 --> 00:22:34,880
(Drive like that?)

447
00:22:41,720 --> 00:22:43,070
(If only)

448
00:22:44,720 --> 00:22:46,440
(Wei Ziqi noticed the danger then...)

449
00:22:46,790 --> 00:22:47,640
Watch out!

450
00:22:47,920 --> 00:22:49,857
(He would definitely
make the car turn left)

451
00:22:50,070 --> 00:22:52,750
(so that his side
will meet with Xi Lin's car.)

452
00:22:53,550 --> 00:22:55,830
(To protect Wei Ziqi, Yuan Xia)

453
00:22:56,310 --> 00:22:58,110
(would definitely let
her side of the car)

454
00:22:58,160 --> 00:22:59,480
(collide with Xi Lin's car.)

455
00:23:00,790 --> 00:23:02,750
(Xi Lin must not have expected)

456
00:23:03,720 --> 00:23:05,510
(that Yuan Xia would protect Wei Ziqi)

457
00:23:05,960 --> 00:23:08,510
(and made her side of the car
face the impact.)

458
00:23:10,110 --> 00:23:11,070
(If that's the case,)

459
00:23:12,750 --> 00:23:16,960
(the one who Xi Lin
wanted to kill is me.)

460
00:23:23,070 --> 00:23:24,240
(From our first time)

461
00:23:24,440 --> 00:23:26,440
(trying to change my ending until now,)

462
00:23:26,550 --> 00:23:27,790
(all our efforts are in vain.)

463
00:23:27,790 --> 00:23:29,400
(It's like the universe is telling us)

464
00:23:29,400 --> 00:23:31,030
(that everything is already fixed)

465
00:23:31,114 --> 00:23:32,457
(so I'm willing to take the risk)

466
00:23:32,790 --> 00:23:33,960
(this time around.)

467
00:23:34,200 --> 00:23:36,200
(I don't want to be frightened anymore.)

468
00:23:47,960 --> 00:23:49,480
Have you really decided to do this?

469
00:23:50,680 --> 00:23:52,070
I still think it's too risky.

470
00:23:52,110 --> 00:23:53,200
What if Xi Lin gets the phone

471
00:23:53,200 --> 00:23:54,480
