472
00:23:54,640 --> 00:23:56,200
After all, if we lose the phone,

473
00:23:56,200 --> 00:23:58,240
we won't be able to change the fact
that Yuan Xia died.

474
00:24:00,680 --> 00:24:01,510
Besides,

475
00:24:01,750 --> 00:24:03,200
how can we make Xi Lin get the phone

476
00:24:03,200 --> 00:24:04,571
without raising her suspicion?

477
00:24:06,510 --> 00:24:08,440
If she really wants to get the phone,

478
00:24:08,885 --> 00:24:10,657
she will definitely do it
by utilizing Chenchen.

479
00:24:11,030 --> 00:24:11,790
Chenchen?

480
00:24:11,960 --> 00:24:13,750
That's Wei Ziqi's
administrative assistant.

481
00:24:14,640 --> 00:24:15,440
No.

482
00:24:15,440 --> 00:24:16,680
As long as Xi Lin holds a concert,

483
00:24:16,680 --> 00:24:19,160
our fan club must give full support.

484
00:24:20,550 --> 00:24:21,960
Fine, that's everything for now.

485
00:24:23,960 --> 00:24:24,750
Xia.

486
00:24:24,750 --> 00:24:25,880
Are you a fan of Xi Lin?

487
00:24:25,880 --> 00:24:26,400
Yes.

488
00:24:26,400 --> 00:24:27,640
I am the president

489
00:24:27,640 --> 00:24:28,480
of her fan club.

490
00:24:28,514 --> 00:24:30,657
When we went to the hospital
to visit Xi Lin before,

491
00:24:30,790 --> 00:24:32,510
the postcard among the flowers
by her bed

492
00:24:32,750 --> 00:24:33,960
has Chenchen's signature.

493
00:24:34,720 --> 00:24:36,790
If Xi Lin intends to steal the phone,

494
00:24:37,310 --> 00:24:38,720
she will definitely use Chenchen.

495
00:24:40,880 --> 00:24:42,750
There's one last problem left.

496
00:24:43,160 --> 00:24:45,030
How do we make
Wei Ziqi from a year later

497
00:24:45,510 --> 00:24:47,030
cooperate with our plan?

498
00:24:52,742 --> 00:24:54,310
Just make a phone call and he'll know.

499
00:24:54,580 --> 00:24:58,500
(2024.12.28 12:00)

500
00:25:03,960 --> 00:25:05,830
There's something I want to tell you.

501
00:25:07,960 --> 00:25:09,720
We may need you to cooperate with us.

502
00:25:17,750 --> 00:25:19,240
This is roughly the plan.

503
00:25:20,200 --> 00:25:21,790
This is the only way

504
00:25:21,790 --> 00:25:23,400
to collect evidence
of Xi Lin's crime.

505
00:25:24,680 --> 00:25:25,550
I won't help you

506
00:25:25,550 --> 00:25:26,720
because it's too dangerous.

507
00:25:27,028 --> 00:25:28,428
(2024, 2025)
Did he also agree?

508
00:25:28,960 --> 00:25:30,240
Even if it's for revenge,

509
00:25:30,240 --> 00:25:32,020
he can't push you out there
and use you as bait.

510
00:25:32,030 --> 00:25:33,400
This has nothing to do with Wei Ziqi.

511
00:25:33,720 --> 00:25:35,310
I decided to do this myself.

512
00:25:35,830 --> 00:25:36,350
Besides,

513
00:25:36,350 --> 00:25:38,240
we have already made
extensive preparations.

514
00:25:38,550 --> 00:25:39,720
You just have to act like

515
00:25:39,720 --> 00:25:41,550
you don't know that
the phone is with Xi Lin

516
00:25:41,550 --> 00:25:42,640
and make a call to her

517
00:25:42,750 --> 00:25:44,750
to give her a heads-up of my death.

518
00:25:45,200 --> 00:25:47,440
How are you going to
solve the fatal danger brought

519
00:25:47,590 --> 00:25:49,310
by the cold and the bellflower allergy

520
00:25:49,440 --> 00:25:50,790
after entering the cold storage?

521
00:25:50,885 --> 00:25:52,309
(2024, 2025)
If it's preserved flowers,

522
00:25:52,310 --> 00:25:54,110
there will be no allergic reaction.

523
00:25:55,030 --> 00:25:56,110
As for the cold storage,

524
00:25:57,790 --> 00:25:58,960
I believe in Ni Ning.

525
00:25:58,960 --> 00:25:59,720
That's not enough.

526
00:26:00,028 --> 00:26:01,714
(2024, 2025)
That's far from enough.

527
00:26:06,400 --> 00:26:07,750
Convey my message to him, please?

528
00:26:08,510 --> 00:26:10,920
Wei Ziqi asked me to tell you something.

529
00:26:12,160 --> 00:26:14,200
I know what he regrets most

530
00:26:15,240 --> 00:26:17,200
and I won't let it happen again.

531
00:26:19,070 --> 00:26:19,920
Tell him this,

532
00:26:20,550 --> 00:26:21,680
and he will help us.

533
00:26:23,480 --> 00:26:24,270
He said

534
00:26:24,400 --> 00:26:26,510
he knows what you regret most

535
00:26:26,640 --> 00:26:28,640
and he won't let the same thing
happen again.

536
00:26:30,310 --> 00:26:31,110
Don't worry,

537
00:26:32,085 --> 00:26:33,800
they will do their best to protect me

538
00:26:34,440 --> 00:26:36,440
the same way you did.

539
00:26:41,680 --> 00:26:42,480
Come in.

540
00:26:45,914 --> 00:26:48,030
Xia, Finance Department
has called you to a meeting.

541
00:26:56,200 --> 00:26:57,350
Let's go.

542
00:27:34,440 --> 00:27:37,310
Yuan Xia, don't speak.
Just listen to what I have to say.

543
00:27:38,030 --> 00:27:39,310
Your future has not changed.

544
00:27:39,720 --> 00:27:41,750
You will still be locked up
in the cold storage

545
00:27:41,920 --> 00:27:43,640
at Lakeside Hotel on December 31st.

546
00:27:43,920 --> 00:27:45,830
I would be pretending
to propose to Xi Lin

547
00:27:45,942 --> 00:27:47,714
in an attempt to get evidence
of Xi Kun's crime.

548
00:27:51,160 --> 00:27:52,030
I will do it myself.

549
00:28:07,940 --> 00:28:09,940
(Yuan Xia)

550
00:28:17,640 --> 00:28:18,440
Wei Ziqi,

551
00:28:18,514 --> 00:28:19,640
I know that you were the one

552
00:28:19,640 --> 00:28:21,070
who called me last night.

