when you didn't speak at first

555
00:28:23,790 --> 00:28:25,160
but I heard you calling me Yuan

556
00:28:25,160 --> 00:28:26,960
when I was hanging up.

557
00:28:27,510 --> 00:28:29,110
I didn't react at first,

558
00:28:29,160 --> 00:28:31,240
but when I passed by the market
and saw a parrot,

559
00:28:31,350 --> 00:28:32,550
it finally hit me

560
00:28:32,720 --> 00:28:34,000
that you are the boy in the attic,

561
00:28:34,000 --> 00:28:34,640
is that right?

562
00:28:34,771 --> 00:28:36,640
You've always known
that I was Yuan, right?

563
00:28:37,057 --> 00:28:39,070
I have something very important
to pass to you.

564
00:28:39,110 --> 00:28:40,920
Wait for me at the hotel.
I'll go find you.

565
00:28:55,510 --> 00:28:56,830
Ziqi, are you ready?

566
00:29:01,200 --> 00:29:01,960
Let's go.

567
00:29:06,220 --> 00:29:07,780
(Xi Lin & Wei Ziqi)

568
00:29:16,960 --> 00:29:18,030
Miss, please sign here.

569
00:29:25,640 --> 00:29:26,440
Hello,

570
00:29:26,880 --> 00:29:28,440
are you Miss Yuan?

571
00:29:30,000 --> 00:29:31,350
A gentleman asked me to tell you

572
00:29:31,350 --> 00:29:33,028
that he is waiting for you
at the restaurant.

573
00:29:33,720 --> 00:29:34,550
Sure, thank you.

574
00:29:34,550 --> 00:29:35,310
You're welcome.

575
00:30:14,030 --> 00:30:15,750
There is still time before your death.

576
00:30:15,750 --> 00:30:17,390
It's the same
as the original time and space.

577
00:30:17,400 --> 00:30:18,270
The only difference is

578
00:30:18,440 --> 00:30:19,480
my engagement with Xi Lin

579
00:30:19,480 --> 00:30:20,960
will become ours.

580
00:30:21,640 --> 00:30:23,440
Pei Shen who killed you
would also be dead.

581
00:30:24,440 --> 00:30:25,790
You must be wary of Xi Lin.

582
00:30:29,590 --> 00:30:30,790
Ziqi, don't worry.

583
00:30:31,510 --> 00:30:33,960
I like the death
you mentioned very much.

584
00:30:35,440 --> 00:30:38,030
(I will definitely give you
a perfect wedding.)

585
00:30:58,651 --> 00:31:02,551
♪I'm not just a passerby♪

586
00:31:03,791 --> 00:31:06,331
♪I'm trying my hardest♪

587
00:31:07,671 --> 00:31:10,121
♪To reunite with you♪

588
00:31:13,741 --> 00:31:17,241
♪If time could testify♪

589
00:31:19,051 --> 00:31:22,391
♪I've searched for it
over and over again♪

590
00:31:22,841 --> 00:31:26,751
♪For the same look in your eyes
as before♪

591
00:31:26,981 --> 00:31:31,441
♪This voiceless yearning
transcends time and space♪

592
00:31:31,561 --> 00:31:35,421
♪Love redeems each other,
never faltering♪

593
00:31:35,601 --> 00:31:39,171
♪How I wish with one turn♪

594
00:31:39,361 --> 00:31:43,681
♪Two could become one♪

595
00:31:44,331 --> 00:31:46,861
♪I believe love can turn♪

596
00:31:46,861 --> 00:31:50,191
♪A thousand possibilities♪

597
00:31:50,431 --> 00:31:53,771
♪Hold you tighter by a fraction♪

598
00:31:53,771 --> 00:31:58,821
♪Just like this until the end of time♪

599
00:31:59,001 --> 00:32:01,271
♪Let love take root♪
